<plot>This long-running news show provided viewers with an in-depth look at the important political, economic and social issues facing the world. Rather than presenting the news in the standard format of being read by an anchor, this show featured one-on-one interviews with newsmakers, documentaries on various subjects, and round-table discussions between a group of experts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?019821</url></doc>
